title: Mimi Mimi!
sinopse:
In a world where human and human beast co-exist, a bureau was established in taking care of human beasts affairs. Kanako Tsuda is a newcomer working in the Health Care Department in the bureau. One day, she was assigned to capture a reported ferocious human beast. In the verge of getting assaulted by a human bureau, she was saved by a human beast—rabbit...

(Source: MU)
